Name: Starfighter: Eclipse
About the game: A Mystery in Deep Space Your mission: join an Alliance surveillance team with Selene, your newly-assigned navigator, to investigate a derelict alien spacecraft. But when you return from the away mission, something is amiss, and it's up to you to figure out why. Along the way, you can interact with Starfighter characters new and old, and maybe attract the attention of your favorite! Explore the Kepler Navigate the difficult politics of the alliance starship Kepler as you explore the beautiful sci-fi backgrounds designed by HamletMachine and the Date Nighto team. Play through all the routes to unlock sexy scenes and bonus art!
